Kinney@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Yol-La-Tengo-Gossip-Sleater0Kinney@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Yol-La-Tengo-Gossip-Sleater0Kinney@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Yol-La-Tengo-Gossip-Sleater0Kinney@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Yol-La-Tengo-Gossip-Sleater0Kinney@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Yol-La-Tengo-Gossip-Sleater0Kinney@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/all-points-east">All Points East</a>宣布了今年的完整阵容，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-postal-service">包括 The Postal Service</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/death-cab-for-cutie">Death Cab For Cutie</a> 。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：本· <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ben-gibbard-interview-death-cab-for-cutie-postal-service-trasatlanticism-give-up-anniversary-new-music-3418335">吉巴德 (Ben Gibbard) 庆祝“死亡出租车”和“邮政服务”成立 20 周年</a></strong></li></ul><p>2024 年的音乐节将回到东伦敦维多利亚公园的老场地，并于 8 月 16 日至 8 月 25 日举办，为期 10 天。</p><p>此前， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-postal-service-death-cab-for-cutie-unveiled-joint-headliners-all-points-east-3555849">The Postal Service 和 Death Cab For Cutie 都被宣布为活动最后一天的头条新闻</a>——两家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/death-cab-for-cutie-and-the-postal-service-tease-london-show-as-they-announce-2024-co-headline-tour-3551457">公司联手进行联合头条巡演</a>，庆祝各自专辑《Give Up》和《Transatlanticism》问世二十周年。</p><p>现在，在最后一天参加音乐节的艺术家的完整名单已经公布，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sleater-kinney">Sleater-Kinney</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yo-la-tengo">Yo La Tengo</a>在内的独立重量级人物也加入了阵容。</p><p>对于前者来说，他们将在本月早些时候发布备受期待的最新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sleater-kinney-little-rope-review-3572467">“Little Rope”</a>之后出现在东伦敦音乐节上。对于后者，Ira Caplan 和 Co. 将把他们标志性的另类摇滚音乐带到 All Points East 舞台，其中包括他们五年来的第一张唱片<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/yo-la-tengo-announce-new-album-this-stupid-world-and-share-single-fallout-3341859">《This Stupid World》</a>中的曲目。</p><p>其他新宣布将于 8 月 25 日星期日演出的乐队包括 Beth Ditto 领导的美国三重奏<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gossip">Gossip</a>以及格莱美奖获奖法国合成流行乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/phoenix">Phoenix</a> 。</p><p>崭露头角的鞋履艺术家<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wednesday">Wednesday</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-decemberists">以及 The Decemberists</a>和伦敦本地人 Soft Launch 也已确认参与其中。您可以在下面的海报中找到周日（8 月 25 日）的完整演出阵容，并<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fall-points-east-tickets%2Fartist%2F5245909" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处购票</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3579837" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3579837" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3579837" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/All-Points-East-2024@2000x2800.jpeg" alt="All Point East 2024，8 月 25 日星期日阵容海报" width="2000" height="2829" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/All-Points-East-2024@2000x2800.jpeg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/All-Points-East-2024@2000x2800-400x566.jpeg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/All-Points-East-2024@2000x2800-800x1132.jpeg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/All-Points-East-2024@2000x2800-696x984.jpeg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/All-Points-East-2024@2000x2800-1392x1969.jpeg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/All-Points-East-2024@2000x2800-1068x1511.jpeg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3579837" class="wp-caption-text"> 2024 年 All Points East，8 月 25 日星期日阵容海报。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>如上所述， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-postal-service-death-cab-for-cutie-unveiled-joint-headliners-all-points-east-3555849">The Postal Service 和 Death Cab For Cutie 早在 2023 年就被宣布为 2024 年 All Points East 最终日期的头条新闻</a>。</p><p>对于他们的联合头条演出，两个乐队的联合创始人本杰明·吉巴德 (Benjamin Gibbard) 将在当晚与两个乐队一起进行双重表演。现场还将完整表演各自的专辑《Give Up》和《Transatlanticism》，以庆祝专辑发行 20 周年。</p><p>对于 The Postal Service 来说，All Points East 的老虎机标志着他们十多年来首次在伦敦亮相。</p><p>今年早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ben-gibbard-interview-death-cab-for-cutie-postal-service-trasatlanticism-give-up-anniversary-new-music-3418335">吉巴德在接受</a><em><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ben-gibbard-interview-death-cab-for-cutie-postal-service-trasatlanticism-give-up-anniversary-new-music-3418335">NME</a></em>采访时谈到了《Give Up》和《Transatlanticism》的 20 周年纪念日，以及即将到来的巡演。 “反思 20 年前的你对于了解今天的你是必要的，”他说。 “我对此很期待。这些记录中没有我不能正面面对的骷髅。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/loyle-carner-confirmed-as-first-headliner-for-londons-all-points-east-2024-3542580">2024 年版的另一位头条人物是获得水星奖提名的 Loyle Carner</a> ，他将于 8 月 17 日星期六登台，与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nas">Nas</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ezra-collective">Ezra Collective</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sainte">Sainté</a>等<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nas-and-ezra-collective-lead-names-to-join-loyle-carner-at-all-points-east-2024-3546546">艺术家一起登台</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3579847" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3579847" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3579847" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Loyle-Carner@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Loyle Carner 出席 2023 年 10 月 12 日在英国伦敦 The House of KOKO 与 Stone Island 合作举办的 Frieze London 20 周年派对" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Loyle-Carner@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Loyle-Carner@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Loyle-Carner@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w,